HEADWORD: nonviolence
<hw>nonviolence</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The theory, doctrine, or
practice of peaceful resistance to a government by fasting or refusing
to cooperate.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> passive resistance.</syn>⟦br⟧
